responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "B28C38654CA9C1B302C98FB48FF965F1", "When treasures grew plenty and pockets were torn, a wish for more space was soon to be born. A Djinn quite old an ancient from lost seas. Beaming out from a lantern with offer decreed. To you I give a chest whose space is like an abyss. Never  will it fill and light as a feather it is. At that very moment a appeared a chest with a feather of gold. Fill it with all treasures the burglar was told. Scoop after scoop, glint after glint. All the treasure inside the box it went. ")
